{"tid":619931,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"外國工作訴苦區","createTime":"2018-04-07T06:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T15:41:18.000Z","uid":72541,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97ced752e9ee0753013eb71ef6f0a0c37e573fc6","tid":619931,"uid":72541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"有無巴打去左外國做野？<br />\n<br />\n岩岩黎左日本做左一個月<br />\n轉左行，差唔多所有野由頭適應<br />\n新呢行同本行related嘅<br />\n但好多野要唔識，成日做錯野<br />\n<br />\n日文唔夠勁成日聽唔明<br />\n同事nice 嘅，但做唔到佢哋捨棄所有情緒的做法<br />\n有時做到攰，嘆氣咗幾聲，又或者坐姿唔太好<br />\n比人聽/見到之後，背後有人講<br />\n絕對無香港咁free<br />\n<br />\n周圍啲同事又好勁好technical<br />\n而家我語言又輸，technical 又輸<br />\n覺得好徬徨<br />\n<br />\n有無海外巴打可以經驗分享？"},{"pid":"6c5a888e94c960bc4743523251ba520ace8b7e93","tid":619931,"uid":169854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b5e54de39f8affa0aa56046bdb9ff4c54244131","tid":619931,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c5a888e94c960bc4743523251ba520ace8b7e93","tid":619931,"uid":169854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"睇名"},{"pid":"4ec38d0140465ac52821ff9245b4145e3c0c1bc5","tid":619931,"uid":169854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T10:32:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffdb9b66d19edd2845939d2095d6d34fdab7fead","tid":619931,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"坐姿唔太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ee75c30bf2c409aaf8ddb1b795b27997644cdd","tid":619931,"uid":114692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7a0c250db7518025aa7102f4f5c9cee5f760bea","tid":619931,"uid":72541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c5a888e94c960bc4743523251ba520ace8b7e93","tid":619931,"uid":169854,"li